text.tspan: Figure 3: Bottom-up generation of lower levels-of-detail.
(a) The octree after points were partitioned into leaf nodes. Inner nodes still empty.
(b) Different view of (a). Empty inner node <0> is populated by voxelizing all its child nodes.
(c) <1> is voxelized next, using points from leaf-node-children but also voxels from inner-node-children.
(e) The octree hiearchy, with voxel-filled inner nodes.
